verbose_text: The introduction of PEX1 cDNA rescued the impaired peroxisome biogenesis in cells from individual F1-II :3, and PEX6 cDNA rescued peroxisome biogenesis in cells from individual F5-II :2 (complementation in 14% or 20% of cells, respectively; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
evidence: PEX1 cDNA rescued the impaired peroxisome biogenesis in cells from individual F1-II:3
